statement:
select
  tbl_7.col_1 as per_id
from
  tbl_7 tbl_7
where
  (
    (
      tbl_7.col_1 IN (
        SELECT
          DISTINCT tbl_8.col_250
        FROM
          tbl_8
        WHERE
          (
            (
              coalesce(tbl_8.col_252 = 30, 0)
            )
          )
          AND (
            (
              lower(tbl_8.col_288) LIKE (
                '%' || lower(
                  replace(
                    replace('ads-first-promo', '_', '\\_'),
                    '%',
                    '\\%'
                  )
                ) || '%'
              )
            )
          )
          AND (null_or_empty(tbl_8.col_289) = 0)
      )
    )
    AND (
      (
        tbl_7.col_149 in (
          select
            distinct alm.col_149 as alm_id
          from
            tbl_6 alm
          where
            1
        )
        OR (tbl_7.col_149 <= 1)
      )
    )
    AND (tbl_7.col_165 = 0)
  )
  AND 1
group by
  per_id
order by
  per_id asc NULLS LAST
